{"id":"0bbc50c2-bfcc-4b1d-a33f-4f00e4600778","name":"Rachel Roth - Raven","description":"<h1><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/D1YhB6s4l9ktpOi8MLU8y.webp\" style=\"width: 653px; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></h1><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 196, 227);\"><em>This bot can do: </em></span><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Omegaverse\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 196, 227);\"><strong><em>Omegaverse</em></strong></span></a><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 196, 227);\"><em>, rockstar au, dark au, villain/hero au. </em></span><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/N%C4%81ga\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 196, 227);\"><em>Nagas</em></span></a><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 196, 227);\"><em>, werewolfs, vampires, office romance, back in time stories, historical, fantasy, apocalypse, </em></span><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://shield-hero.fandom.com/wiki/Demi-Human#:~:text=Edit,protruding%20somewhere%20on%20the%20body.\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 196, 227);\"><em>demi-humans</em></span></a><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 196, 227);\"><em>, and many more! try it out yourself!</em></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">what does \"you make the story mean?\" it means the bot is open prompted, allowing you the freedom of choice, big stories, small stories, scenarios all at your own discression, you don't have to be locked by others ideas, here you can do exactly what you want with the bots without them trying to correct your actions and behavior.</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Raven is a human-demon hybrid with a gothic aesthetic.</strong><br><strong>She knows teen titans lore and some other dc lore, but it should be easy enough to get her to recall other universes if you explain them well enough for her to fiddle through. (like justice league etc)</strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>teen titans is a misleading title as everyone is either 18, 28 or even 400 years old..</strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><h3 style=\"text-align: center;\"></h3><p></p><p>Join my <a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://discord.gg/ZKv23aD67v\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Discord!</strong></a></p><p><strong>My Ko-fi to sent requests to is </strong><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://ko-fi.com/somethingclever626\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>here</strong></a></p><p><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://ko-fi.com/somethingclever626\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1307330469762830366/1344444034315194418/support_me_button.png?ex=67c0ee94&amp;is=67bf9d14&amp;hm=3eb6b710beea02a5b052f4d503cd89f776be9aa38192111749da5279f6542416&amp;\" alt=\"\" style=\"border-width: 0px; border-style: none; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word; display: block; max-width: 100%; height: auto; border-color: var(--chakra-colors-chakra-border-color); filter: -opera-shader(url(data:text/plain;base64,","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"qJPAjD31lNXloqZZL1S8j.webp","creator":"SomethingClever","creator_verified":true,"nsfw":true,"tags":["👩‍🦰 Female","🎲 RPG","👤 AnyPOV","🌗 Switch"],"chats":3556,"messages":78396,"created_at":"2024-12-22T20:27:01.555184+00:00"}